dia src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645748001407057/IMG_9780.jpg?ex=69ec2436&amp;is=69ead2b6&amp;hm=6142827bc64555e026867f63c696619a971af813f94aac5a7158a4624d1c3370&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_9780.jpg (321.48 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645748655722535/IMG_9779.jpg?ex=69ec2436&amp;is=69ead2b6&amp;hm=0d0097b4931a4465041d3d260e27ca6df4a89f6b0838cf7f708c6441ab059f63&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645748655722535/IMG_9779.jpg?ex=69ec2436&amp;is=69ead2b6&amp;hm=0d0097b4931a4465041d3d260e27ca6df4a89f6b0838cf7f708c6441ab059f63&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_9779.jpg (320.64 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645749146320906/IMG_9777.jpg?ex=69ec2436&amp;is=69ead2b6&amp;hm=a8ac78c8c67baba2a5360926036c30262b1a278e99c46e954841a39698d20394&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645749146320906/IMG_9777.jpg?ex=69ec2436&amp;is=69ead2b6&amp;hm=a8ac78c8c67baba2a5360926036c30262b1a278e99c46e954841a39698d20394&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: IMG_9777.jpg (371.38 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>", "<div class=chatlog__attachment><a href=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645749553303625/signal-2026-01-07-181636.jpg?ex=69ec2437&amp;is=69ead2b7&amp;hm=3aa0c14b526f1cf3f47b36f03faa4aedb59c25dd4a68f2bd509e8e7259d85672&amp;\"> <img class=chatlog__attachment-media src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1458180906069262436/1458645749553303625/signal-2026-01-07-181636.jpg?ex=69ec2437&amp;is=69ead2b7&amp;hm=3aa0c14b526f1cf3f47b36f03faa4aedb59c25dd4a68f2bd509e8e7259d85672&amp;\" alt=\"Image attachment\" title=\"Image: signal-2026-01-07-181636.jpg (344.33 KB)\" loading=lazy> </a></div>"], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1458666387391123556", "author": "ded (SalishMesh)", "author_handle": "dedskelly", "user_id": "279655580174516234", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, January 7, 2026 10:39 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-07 10:39 p.m.", "text": "Newest one is on the forge", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Newest one is on the forge</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459559233841528977", "author": "Symbioquine", "author_handle": "symbioquine_03306", "user_id": "761399281948295169", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 10, 2026 9:47 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-10 9:47 a.m.", "text": "This is great!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>This is great!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459758422500049190", "author": "ded (SalishMesh)", "author_handle": "dedskelly", "user_id": "279655580174516234", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, January 10, 2026 10:58 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-10 10:58 p.m.", "text": "There is a mailing list in the repo readme, and the OP here (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>There is a mailing list in the repo readme, and the OP here</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, January 10, 2026 11:01 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=symbioquine_03306>Symbioquine</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1459560006100979833')\"> Few points of feedback (since I can&#39;t seem to log into the repo site to create issues):\n<ul><li>Would be nice to have ping option for repeaters (and opening the DM UI isn&#39;t very useful for repeaters)</li><li>Much lower priority (and harder) would be nice to have admin UI for repeaters</li><li>Touch input is way better than the reference MeshCore firmware, but still fairly finicky (not sure if this is just down to the hardware or if it can be improved in software)</li><li>Keyboard input is spotty with keys often not registering even when spammed, then working fine a few seconds later</li><li>I don&#39;t see a way to remove contacts via the current on-device UI (other than presumably exporting/modifying/re-importing the config via JSON</li><li>Attempting to remove a contact when using the T-Deck as a companion via the MeshCore app results in an error</li><li>UI is glitchy when scrolling sometimes (will post screencap shortly)</li></ul> </span> <span class=chatlog__reply-edited-timestamp title=\"Saturday, January 10, 2026 10:05 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459907760308093039", "author": "Symbioquine", "author_handle": "symbioquine_03306", "user_id": "761399281948295169", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 8:52 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 8:52 a.m.", "text": "I'll have to look into Forgejo since I self-host a GitLab instance, but it's always seemed ridiculously heavy-weight and I'm always playing catch-up on the maintenance.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;ll have to look into Forgejo since I self-host a GitLab instance, but it&#39;s always seemed ridiculously heavy-weight and I&#39;m always playing catch-up on the maintenance.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=dedskelly>ded (SalishMesh)</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1459758472878096549')\"> But ya its a private instance </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459920054098464918", "author": "ded (SalishMesh)", "author_handle": "dedskelly", "user_id": "279655580174516234", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 9:41 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 9:41 a.m.", "text": "it's the new gitea, but we don't have federation enabled", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>it&#39;s the new gitea, but we don&#39;t have federation enabled</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=symbioquine_03306>Symbioquine</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1459907760308093039')\"> I&#39;ll have to look into Forgejo since I self-host a GitLab instance, but it&#39;s always seemed ridiculously heavy-weight and I&#39;m always playing catch-up on the maintenance. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459920717217927309", "author": "Symbioquine", "author_handle": "symbioquine_03306", "user_id": "761399281948295169", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 9:43 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 9:43 a.m.", "text": "I'd need to see if the OIDC integration is up to snuff, but I assume that's table stakes in 2025 2026 🫣", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;d need to see if the OIDC integration is up to snuff, but I assume that&#39;s table stakes in <s>2025</s> 2026 &#129763;</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=dedskelly>ded (SalishMesh)</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1459920054098464918')\"> it&#39;s the new gitea, but we don&#39;t have federation enabled </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459920900689232034", "author": "Symbioquine", "author_handle": "symbioquine_03306", "user_id": "761399281948295169", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/761399281948295169/9899436c9eb24cb510b339c10145f83d.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 9:44 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 9:44 a.m.", "text": "Sadly, I'm pretty attached to the web UI issue management stuff personally (for my own projects that is)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Sadly, I&#39;m pretty attached to the web UI issue management stuff personally (for my own projects that is)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=dedskelly>ded (SalishMesh)</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1459920182079393898')\"> i want to go back to just git repos, no web junk. email and git </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459940406958755999", "author": "ded (SalishMesh)", "author_handle": "dedskelly", "user_id": "279655580174516234", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 11:01 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 11:01 a.m.", "text": "Open ID works though", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Open ID works though</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459951722452750346", "author": "skykingisepic", "author_handle": "skykingisepic", "user_id": "1092980540749139988", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1092980540749139988/08e1c5b4a539322bee7416f800a73b69.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 11:46 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 11:46 a.m.", "text": "Ooh, very nice. Cloned, built, and flashed. Working. Auto adds discovered contacts. Sends and receives msgs. Sends adverts. Screen doesn't fully display on wake, need to move trackballl around to paint enough to select any menu option for screen to fully display. Battery charge pct seems off. Previous msgs for Contact not showing sometimes, go back and tap contact until msgs show.. Minor issues for a first go. Nice job. (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Ooh, very nice. Cloned, built, and flashed. Working. Auto adds discovered contacts. Sends and receives msgs. Sends adverts. Screen doesn&#39;t fully display on wake, need to move trackballl around to paint enough to select any menu option for screen to fully display. Battery charge pct seems off. Previous msgs for Contact not showing sometimes, go back and tap contact until msgs show.. Minor issues for a first go. Nice job.</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Sunday, January 11, 2026 11:52 a.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1459954582456373492", "author": "ded (SalishMesh)", "author_handle": "dedskelly", "user_id": "279655580174516234", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/279655580174516234/96af2cf5f9ff55d3c2dbc375f272d25a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, January 11, 2026 11:58 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-11 11:58 a.m.", "text": "Please send feedback to the mailing list", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-pr